---
---

<section id="why-us" aria-labelledby="why-us-heading" class="py-30 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2
      id="why-us-heading"
      class="text-[28px] md:text-[40px] font-semibold leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em] text-[#0a0a0a] mb-4 text-center"
    >
      Why Apex Code
    </h2>
    <p class="text-base font-normal leading-relaxed text-[#555555] text-center mb-14 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Two founders. No account managers. You work directly with the people building your product.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-[#0a0a0a] mb-2">Human Touch</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed text-[#555555]">
          Direct access to the founders who built your solution — no tickets, no handoffs, no delays.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-[#0a0a0a] mb-2">Fast Delivery</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed text-[#555555]">
          We scope tightly and ship in weeks, not quarters. You see working software early and often.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-[#0a0a0a] mb-2">Modern Stack</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed text-[#555555]">
          We use current tools — AI APIs, TypeScript, cloud-native infrastructure — so your solution doesn't age out.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="founder-card">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-[#0a0a0a] mb-3">Vlad Vulcu</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed text-[#555555]">
          Full-stack developer with deep experience in AI integration and backend systems.
          Obsessed with building things that actually work in production, not just in demos.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="founder-card">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-[#0a0a0a] mb-2">Mihnea Mihai</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed text-[#555555]">
          Product-minded engineer who bridges the gap between what clients need and what
          gets built. Focused on shipping fast without cutting corners.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .feature-card {
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 150ms ease, box-shadow 150ms ease;
  }
  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
  }
  .founder-card {
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 150ms ease, box-shadow 150ms ease;
  }
  .founder-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
  }
</style>
